{
  "stem": "18581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- afterwards, some of them were young people, university students, that I met at university.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With some of them, I even continued my friendship in Israel afterwards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew plenty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we knew from history, Lithuania being on the-- at the crossroads between east and west, we knew all about [NON-ENGLISH], the push towards the east.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans wanted some [NON-ENGLISH]-- they needed more space.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to subject the Slav countries, mainly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is, Poland and Russia, use their people that they regarded as subhumans--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--destroy the Jews and the-- and the gypsies, and-- and create more space for-- for-- for Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not we.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe there were some with-- with really elaborate radios, but--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we knew, of course, Great Britain enjoyed, in the Jewish community, and the-- a very high standard of-- how shall I say-- a-- a-- a very high [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they were-- said, oh, as British Empire, you know, a quarter of the world belongs to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The sun never sets on the British Empire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we thought, also, the-- the British character, you know--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--will somehow, hopefully, prevail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, we were worried because we see-- we saw what Hitler did, and how easily he destroyed the French army for the second time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same way, by circumventing the Maginot Line and going through Belgium and Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we were very worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Lithuania was a rich country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Farmers were very productive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no shortage of any kind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the contrary, in the first few months, there was a kind of a little boom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because people were worried about what might happen, and because they-- we knew the jokes about, you know, the lack of matches the lack of other things in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
